title: Intervention S03E09 - Ashley
description: Ashley, the all-american girl, Deacon's daughter, and high school athlete turned addict. When she's not indulging in black tar heroin or crushing Xanax, she is actively finding ways to get money for her high, leading her into risky situations with drug dealers. Already battling respiratory distress from her addiction, this young lady is on the brink. Her background is heartbreaking; her present (in this episode) is dismal. Intervention, Season 3, Episode 9 will tell you what her future holds.
